WEBVTT

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:47.600
You look so much like your mother Lingwu,

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:49.920
almost identical.

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:52.000
Well,

00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:55.400
do you know who killed my parents?

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.440
I only remember

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:02.080
that your parents died on the young master's 18th birthday.

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:05.600
Today is my beloved son Silin's birthday.

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.440
Thank you all for coming.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:08.840
Have a drink.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:10.280
Thank you.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:14.920
That day, Mrs. Liu gave your mother a wooden box.

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:18.600
A wooden box?

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.620
What kind of wooden box was it?

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:24.160
I vaguely remember that wooden box was special.

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:27.280
There was an evening primrose carved on the lid.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:29.960
Evening primrose?

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:31.800
That day...

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:34.120
We were extremely busy.

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:38.500
The master was preparing for the young master's birthday.

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:40.280
It was quite hectic.

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:42.300
Many distinguished guests came.

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:46.280
We didn't hear about your parents until that evening.

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:49.759
Did anything else happen that day?

00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:51.400
Oh, right.

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:56.920
I remember a young maid named Xiuhe also had an incident.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.000
Xiuhe?

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:03.080
She was found dead in a pond.

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:07.040
It was discovered right around the same time as your parents' incident.

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:09.970
When they found her, her body was pale from the water.

00:02:10.039 --> 00:02:12.240
There was also a bullet hole in her head.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:14.920
Who knows who she offended.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.840
So young.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.240
Such a pity.

00:02:19.760 --> 00:02:23.000
I don't know if she had any family left.

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:36.360
Zixin.

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:39.840
Zixin.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.360
Ah!

00:02:41.640 --> 00:02:42.760
Are you alright?

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:45.040
Ah, I'm fine.

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:50.360
I remember when you first came to the Liu residence, you called me Xiuhe.

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.960
Could it be that you knew her?

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:55.960
To be honest with you.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.320
Actually, Xiuhe

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.240
is my cousin.

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:03.040
She's your cousin?

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.890
So you came to the Liu residence to find the real culprit.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:09.240
That's right.

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:12.120
Zixin.

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:14.040
Don't be sad.

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:16.880
The dead cannot come back to life.

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:20.880
But I believe one day the murderer will be brought to justice.

00:03:25.320 --> 00:03:26.240
Yiyu.

00:03:26.680 --> 00:03:27.600
Thank you.

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.040
I...

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:33.480
I'll go now. Be careful.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.600
What are you doing?

00:03:57.880 --> 00:03:59.840
You've already forgotten the slap

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:01.680
you owe me so soon?

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:07.040
You really have thick skin.

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:09.240
My hand hurt from slapping you.

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:14.960
You do have some charm,

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:17.320
but you're nothing but common trash.

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:19.600
How dare you compare yourself to me?

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:25.760
If I killed you,

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:28.170
certain people would be heartbroken.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:30.240
I'll give you a cold shower instead,

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:32.040
to help you come to your senses

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:34.480
and see your true worth.

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:35.760
Pour!

00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:51.600
Look at you, like a drowned rat

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:54.240
and still acting proud in front of me.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.000
Sinan.

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.880
Sinan, don't go.

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:43.320
How long have I been asleep?

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.659
Three days and nights.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.000
Eat this.

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:52.560
You've been taking care of me all this time?

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:53.880
Of course.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.330
I'm the one who brought you back after all.

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:58.620
You must be hungry.

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:05.600
Open your mouth.

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:20.160
Is it good?

00:07:35.159 --> 00:07:36.040
Commander Xu,

00:07:36.159 --> 00:07:38.840
I'm truly grateful to you this time.

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:40.440
Without your help,

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:43.480
this shipment would never have made it into Yun City.

00:07:43.480 --> 00:07:44.120
Here,

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:45.960
let me toast to both of you.

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:47.480
Second Master.

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.159
Come.

00:07:52.600 --> 00:07:56.320
Mr. Sun, you're being too polite.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:59.480
I, Commander Xu, should be the one thanking you.

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:03.400
Everyone thinks being a commander is so impressive,

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:07.240
with hundreds of men and guns under my command.

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:11.440
But who knows that I have so many mouths to feed,

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:12.760
and horses to feed too?

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:13.280
Yes, indeed.

00:08:13.280 --> 00:08:17.560
Every day I wake up to nothing but expenses.

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:22.120
You've really saved me from a desperate situation.

00:08:22.760 --> 00:08:24.280
Not at all.

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:29.120
Exactly.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:32.320
I really must thank young Sinan.

00:08:32.480 --> 00:08:34.600
If not for his intelligence and capability,

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:37.530
we wouldn't have had this opportunity to cooperate.

00:08:38.679 --> 00:08:40.559
The Commander is absolutely right.

00:08:40.559 --> 00:08:43.320
You've found yourself an excellent son-in-law.

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:46.890
Sinan is a talented young man, not to be underestimated.

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:48.400
Second Master, you're too kind.

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:49.560
In business,

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:52.040
I still have much to learn from you.

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:55.280
Come, Second Master, let's drink up.

00:08:55.560 --> 00:08:56.040
Good.

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:56.880
