00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.880
What a good drinker!

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:06.780
By the way, Commander, Sinan,

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:13.840
here's your share of the profits.

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:30.640
Commander, Sinan, rest assured,

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:32.760
next time it will be even more.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.440
Sinan.

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:42.320
You're much more open-minded than that stubborn father of yours.

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.640
We're in business.

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.560
We do whatever makes money.

00:09:45.560 --> 00:09:47.320
Why bother with so many rules?

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:50.880
Your father is just too stubborn and rigid.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.240
That's why...

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:55.880
I prefer working with people like the Second Young Master.

00:09:55.880 --> 00:09:57.760
He's got brains. Come, come.

00:09:58.560 --> 00:10:00.320
Let's have another drink.

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:01.680
Come, come.

