Madam.

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:15.760
Someone outside the mansion asked me to give you this letter.

00:10:26.680 --> 00:10:27.440
Yiyu.

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:30.320
Master Zhang died of a sudden heart attack last night.

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:31.880
I've asked the neighbors around.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:34.410
